text: Artocarpus rubrovenia is a species of plant in the family Moraceae. It is endemic to the Philippines. It is threatened by habitat loss.World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998. Artocarpus rubrovenus. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 20 August 2007.
